{"type": "article", "id": 23873, "title": "明尼苏达州鸟类插图设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-15T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608131845BmbHL8YeytO2Pp6g.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组关于鸟类的插图设计，美国明尼阿波利斯的设计师 Tony Buckland 根据明尼苏达州的 24 种常见鸟类设计，每种鸟都可看做不同的几何图形组成，鸟的身体是梯形的，鼻子是三角形，通过不同的颜色突出其个性特征，又保持了一种整体的极简美感。这些图案都可以出售，售价 20 美元起，这里是<a href=\"http://www.birdsofminnesota.com/\">网站主页</a>和<a href=\"https://society6.com/tonybuckland\">购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131843TIe5CnBYEvPLMzcj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081318433KoGb5gce9SQsJvx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131843IPnH7AZXSkWawGj2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131844M4Kq6OyNQ0aJWlwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606081318448cpevUhxK94qZE1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73349633\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}